rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:genus? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:class is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_CLASS_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:class?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:class? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:subtribe is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:subtribe was found as a value at the rank of subtribe by the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT bdq:sourceAuthority default = "GBIF Backbone Taxonomy" [https://doi.org/10.15468/39omei],API endpoint [https://api.gbif.org/v1/species?datasetKey=d7dddbf4-2cf0-4f39-9b2a-bb099caae36c&name=]
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_SUBTRIBE_FOUND

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:subtribe occur at rank of Subtribe in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:subtribe occur at rank of Subtribe in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:tribe is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:tribe was found as a value at the rank of tribe by the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT bdq:sourceAuthority default = "GBIF Backbone Taxonomy" [https://doi.org/10.15468/39omei],API endpoint [https://api.gbif.org/v1/species?datasetKey=d7dddbf4-2cf0-4f39-9b2a-bb099caae36c&name=]
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_TRIBE_FOUND

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:tribe occur at rank of Tribe in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:tribe occur at rank of Tribe in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:superfamily is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:superfamily was found as a value at the rank of superfamily by the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT bdq:sourceAuthority default = "GBIF Backbone Taxonomy" [https://doi.org/10.15468/39omei],API endpoint [https://api.gbif.org/v1/species?datasetKey=d7dddbf4-2cf0-4f39-9b2a-bb099caae36c&name=]
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_SUPERFAMILY_FOUND

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:superfamily occur at rank of Superfamily in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:superfamily occur at rank of Superfamily in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:taxonID is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if (1) taxonID is a validly formed LSID, or (2) taxonID is a validly formed URN with at least NID and NSS present, or (3) taxonID is in the form scope:value, or (4) taxonID is a validly formed URI with host and path where path consists of more than just "/"; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_TAXONID_COMPLETE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:taxonID contain a complete identifier?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:taxonID contain a complete identifier? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if either dwc:dateIdentified or dwc:eventDate are empty or are not interpretable as ISO 8601-1:2019 dates; COMPLIANT if dwc:dateIdentified is equal to or is later than dwc:eventDate; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_DATEIDENTIFIED_AFTEREVENTDATE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the date of identification equal to, or later than the dwc:eventDate?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the date of identification equal to, or later than the dwc:eventDate? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:namePublishedInYear is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:namePublishedInYear is interpretable as a year between 1753 and the current year, inclusive
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_NAMEPUBLISHEDINYEAR_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The value of dwc:namePublishedInYear is between 1753-01-01 date and the current date, inclusive
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: The value of dwc:namePublishedInYear is between 1753-01-01 date and the current date, inclusive Validation for SingleRecord
